Episodes.Title: Diego Reunites Hippo & Oxpecker
Episodes.Plot: Hippopotamus is moving to a new home at Hippo Lake, but he needs help from Diego and you to rescue his "symbiotic" friend Oxpecker, who's stuck back at the old river!

Episodes.Title: Diego's Orangutan Rescue
Episodes.Plot: When playful Baby Orangutan gets taken away in a canoe by a rapid river in Borneo, Diego needs to team up with Big Sister Orangutan and you to save him!

Episodes.Title: Where is Okapi's Brother?
Episodes.Plot: Diego, Alicia and Baby Jaguar travel to the African rainforest to visit the okapis. During a game of hide-and-seek, Okapi's brother hids too well and gets lost! It's up to Diego to find him!

Episodes.Title: Puffin Fish Adventure
Episodes.Plot: Bundle up for adventure in Greenland as you and Diego help Puffy the Puffin lead the baby puffins to a fishy snack.

Episodes.Title: Diego's Ringed Seal Rescue
Episodes.Plot: It's an adventure in the Arctic when Diego needs to bring a baby ringed seal back to the Ringed Seal Rescue Home!

Episodes.Title: All Aboard the Giant Panda Express!
Episodes.Plot: Hop aboard the Giant Panda Express to help Diego and Baby Jaguar find a family of pandas in China and bring them to their new home on Bamboo Mountain.

Episodes.Title: Bengal Tiger Makes a Wish
Episodes.Plot: Diego must help Benji the Bengal tiger find his way to the wishing tree where he is supposed to meet his mother.

Episodes.Title: Leaping Lemurs!
Episodes.Plot: To Make a Sifaka Lemur smile really big, Diego and Baby Jaguar need to help her find family in Madagascar. Will You Help too?

Episodes.Title: Diego Saves the Beavers
Episodes.Plot: When a giant wave threatens some beavers and other animals in the Canadian Rockies, Diego and Billy the Beaver need to work together with you for a river rescue

Episodes.Title: Ocean Animal Rescuer
Episodes.Plot: Baby Humpback is in danger after an oil spill in the ocean

Episodes.Title: Welcome Home, Lion Cub
Episodes.Plot: Travel to Africa with Diego and Baby Jaguar to help Daddy Lion and his family make it back to their pride in time for Lion Cub's party.

Episodes.Title: Diego's International Rescue League
Episodes.Plot: Diego leads a team of expert animal rescuers, and together they return five eggs to their habitats and earn their World Rescuers' patches.

Episodes.Title: Diego Rescues Prince Vicuna
Episodes.Plot: Diego must rescue the missing Prince Vicuna and return him to vicuna valley.

Episodes.Title: Koala's Birthday Hug
Episodes.Plot: Diego must rescue a koala who is stuck in the middle of the road.

Episodes.Title: To Babysit a Bobo
Episodes.Plot: Diego must help the Bobo brothers find their three little sisters.

Episodes.Title: Pampas Cat and Friends Help the Rescue Center
Episodes.Plot: A Pampas cat needs Diego's help to find her kittens.

Episodes.Title: Fiercest Animals!
Episodes.Plot: Diego tells Rosita and Martin about the five fiercest animals that he has ever rescued.

Episodes.Title: Cotton-Top Tamarin Cave Rescue
Episodes.Plot: When the Bobos block the exit of a cave, Diego must find another way out.
